      • PermissionChange

        public PermissionChange()

      • PermissionChange

        public PermissionChange(String realmUrl,
                        String userId,
                        Boolean mayRead,
                        Boolean mayWrite,
                        Boolean mayManage)
        Construct a Permission Change Object.
        Parameters:
        realmUrl - Realm to change permissions for. Use * to change the permissions of all Realms.
        userId - User or users to effect. Use * to change the permissions for all users.
        mayRead - Define read access. true or false to request this new value. null to keep current value.
        mayWrite - Define write access. true or false to request this new value. null to keep current value.
        mayManage - Define manage access. true or false to request this new value. null to keep current value.
        See Also:
        Controlling Permissions
